name: Game of Thrones
imdb_description: Nine noble families fight for control over the lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for millennia.

name: Prison Break
imdb_description: Due to a political conspiracy, an innocent man is sent to death row and his only hope is his brother, who makes it his mission to deliberately get himself sent to the same prison in order to break the both of them out, from the inside.

name: Vikings
imdb_description: Vikings transports us to the brutal and mysterious world of Ragnar Lothbrok, a Viking warrior and farmer who yearns to explore--and raid--the distant shores across the ocean.

name: The Boys
imdb_description: A group of vigilantes set out to take down corrupt superheroes who abuse their superpowers.

name: The Mandalorian
imdb_description: The travels of a lone bounty hunter in the outer reaches of the galaxy, far from the authority of the New Republic.

name: The Witcher
imdb_description: Geralt of Rivia, a solitary monster hunter, struggles to find his place in a world where people often prove more wicked than beasts.

name: Money Heist

name: Squid Game
imdb_description: Hundreds of cash-strapped players accept a strange invitation to compete in children's games. Inside, a tempting prize awaits with deadly high stakes. A survival game that has a whopping 45.6 billion-won prize at stake.

name: Daredevil
imdb_description: A blind lawyer by day, vigilante by night. Matt Murdock fights the crime of New York as Daredevil.

name: Arrow
imdb_description: Spoiled billionaire playboy Oliver Queen is missing and presumed dead when his yacht is lost at sea. He returns five years later a changed man, determined to clean up the city as a hooded vigilante armed with a bow.

name: Attack on Titan
imdb_description: After his hometown is destroyed and his mother is killed, young Eren Jaeger vows to cleanse the earth of the giant humanoid Titans that have brought humanity to the brink of extinction.

name: The Last of Us
imdb_description: After a global pandemic destroys civilization, a hardened survivor takes charge of a 14-year-old girl who may be humanity's last hope.

name: The Flash
imdb_description: After being struck by lightning, Barry Allen wakes up from his coma to discover he's been given the power of super speed, becoming the Flash, and fighting crime in Central City.

name: WandaVision
imdb_description: Blends the style of classic sitcoms with the MCU, in which Wanda Maximoff and Vision - two super-powered beings living their ideal suburban lives - begin to suspect that everything is not as it seems.

name: Loki
imdb_description: The mercurial villain Loki resumes his role as the God of Mischief in a new series that takes place after the events of “Avengers: Endgame.”

name: Avatar: The Last Airbender
imdb_description: In a war-torn world of elemental magic, a young boy reawakens to undertake a dangerous mystic quest to fulfill his destiny as the Avatar, and bring peace to the world.

name: The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power

name: House of the Dragon
imdb_description: An internal succession war within House Targaryen at the height of its power, 172 years before the birth of Daenerys Targaryen.

name: The Umbrella Academy
imdb_description: A family of former child heroes, now grown apart, must reunite to continue to protect the world.

name: Spartacus
imdb_description: The life of Spartacus, the gladiator who lead a rebellion against the Romans. From his time as an ally of the Romans, to his betrayal and becoming a gladiator, to the rebellion he leads and its ultimate outcome.

name: The Punisher
imdb_description: After his revenge on those who murdered his family, aimless Marine veteran Frank Castle finds a new meaning in life as a vigilante known as "The Punisher".

name: Moon Knight
imdb_description: Steven Grant discovers he's been granted the powers of an Egyptian moon god. But he soon finds out that these newfound powers can be both a blessing and a curse to his troubled life.

name: Gotham
imdb_description: The story behind Detective James Gordon's rise to prominence in Gotham City in the years before Batman's arrival.

name: The Falcon and the Winter Soldier
imdb_description: Following the events of 'Avengers: Endgame,' Sam Wilson/Falcon and Bucky Barnes/Winter Soldier team up in a global adventure that tests their abilities -- and their patience.

name: Arcane

name: Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.
imdb_description: The missions of the Strategic Homeland Intervention, Enforcement and Logistics Division.

name: Jessica Jones
imdb_description: Following the tragic end of her brief superhero career, Jessica Jones tries to rebuild her life as a private investigator, dealing with cases involving people with remarkable abilities in New York City.

name: Obi-Wan Kenobi

name: Cobra Kai
imdb_description: Decades after their 1984 All Valley Karate Tournament bout, a middle-aged Daniel LaRusso and Johnny Lawrence find themselves martial-arts rivals again.

name: Hawkeye
imdb_description: Series based on the Marvel Comics superhero Hawkeye, centering on the adventures of Young Avenger, Kate Bishop, who took on the role after the original Avenger, Clint Barton.
Counter Terrorism Agent Jack Bauer races against the clock to subvert terrorist plots and save his nation from ultimate disaster.

name: Person of Interest
imdb_description: An ex-CIA agent and a wealthy programmer save lives via a surveillance AI that sends them the identities of civilians involved in impending crimes. However, the details of the crimes, including the civilians' roles, are left a mystery.

name: Love, Death & Robots

name: Altered Carbon

name: Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood

name: Rome
imdb_description: A down-to-earth account of the lives of both illustrious and ordinary Romans set in the last days of the Roman Republic.

name: She-Hulk: Attorney at Law
imdb_description: Jennifer Walters navigates the complicated life of a single, 30-something attorney who also happens to be a green 6-foot-7-inch superpowered Hulk.

name: Battlestar Galactica

name: One Punch Man

name: The Book of Boba Fett

name: Archer

name: Teen Wolf

name: NCIS

name: Buffy the Vampire Slayer

name: Invincible

name: The Last Kingdom

name: Jack Ryan

name: Chuck

name: Spartacus: Gods of the Arena

name: One Piece

name: Dragon Ball Z

name: Reacher

name: Naruto: Shippuden

name: Iron Fist

name: Andor

name: Smallville

name: Star Trek: Discovery

name: Supergirl

name: The Legend of Korra

name: Star Trek: The Next Generation

name: Cowboy Bebop

name: Killing Eve

name: What If...?

name: Banshee

name: Black Sails

name: Batman: The Animated Series

name: Titans

name: Stargate SG-1

name: The Terminal List

name: Falling Skies

name: The Family Man

name: Sacred Games

name: Barry

name: See

imdb_description: In the 23rd Century, Captain James T. Kirk and the crew of the U.S.S. Enterprise explore the galaxy and defend the United Federation of Planets.

name: Dragon Ball Z

name: Star Trek: Picard

name: Battlestar Galactica

name: Burn Notice

name: Blindspot

name: Ash vs Evil Dead

name: Neon Genesis Evangelion

name: Fullmetal Alchemist

name: Angel

name: Star Trek: Voyager

name: Code Geass

name: Castlevania

name: Stargate: Atlantis

name: Halo

name: Shadowhunters

name: Star Trek: Deep Space Nine

name: Disenchantment

name: Sleepy Hollow

name: Continuum

name: Dragon Ball

name: The Last Ship

name: Dragon Ball

name: Bleach

name: CSI: Miami

name: Jericho

name: Snowpiercer

name: Scorpion

name: Doom Patrol

name: Samurai Jack

name: Star Trek: Enterprise

name: All of Us Are Dead

name: Sweet Tooth

name: Dirk Gently's Holistic Detective Agency

name: Nikita

name: Alias

name: Warrior Nun

name: Fate: The Winx Saga

name: Samurai Champloo

name: Almost Human

name: Vikings: Valhalla

name: Dracula

name: Kingdom

name: Regular Show

name: Justice League

name: Sword Art Online

name: CSI: NY

name: Star Wars: Rebels

name: Batwoman

name: Timeless

name: X-Men: The Animated Series

name: Pokémon

name: Defiance
